# Total cards
ggplot(cards, aes(x = City_dist, y = total)) +
  geom_point(size = 2) +
  geom_smooth(method = lm) +
  labs(x = "Distance to urban center (km)", 
    y = "Total Cardenolides") +
  xlim(0, 71) +
  ylim(0,0.8)
## `geom_smooth()` using formula 'y ~ x'
